      "instruction": "<p>Cut  A3 size sheets of <strong>baking paper</strong> (or tin foil)</p><p>Divide the<strong> pepper</strong> <strong>strips </strong>and the<strong> pak choi green tops </strong>and <strong>chopped white bases </strong>evenly between the sheets</p>",
