    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slightly scrunch the edges of the paper around the filling and then add the <strong>Thai-style curry stock </strong>evenly between each parcel</p><p>Scrunch the edges of the <strong>baking paper</strong> around the fish to form a sealed parcel and add to a baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 17 min or until the fish is cooked through and the veg has softened – this is your <strong>Thai-style hake & veg</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
